Perform the filtering

B3[["percent_mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(B3, pattern = "^MT-")
B4[["percent_mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(B4, pattern = "^MT-")
B5[["percent_mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(B5, pattern = "^MT-")
T3[["percent_mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(T3, pattern = "^MT-")
T4[["percent_mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(T4, pattern = "^MT-")
T5[["percent_mt"]] <- PercentageFeatureSet(T5, pattern = "^MT-")

B3 <- subset(B3, subset = nFeature_RNA < 5000 & nFeature_RNA > 200  & nCount_RNA < 25000 & percent_mt < 7)
B4 <- subset(B4, subset = nFeature_RNA < 3000 & nFeature_RNA > 200 & nCount_RNA < 3500 & percent_mt < 7)
B5 <- subset(B5, subset = nFeature_RNA < 3000 & nFeature_RNA > 200 & nCount_RNA < 1500 & percent_mt < 7)

T3 <- subset(T3, subset = nFeature_RNA < 4000 & nFeature_RNA > 200 & nCount_RNA < 10000 & percent_mt < 7)
T4 <- subset(T4, subset = nFeature_RNA < 10000 & nFeature_RNA > 200 & nCount_RNA < 50000 & percent_mt < 7)
T5 <- subset(T5, subset = nFeature_RNA < 6000 & nFeature_RNA > 200 & nCount_RNA < 30000 & percent_mt < 7)
